{"tid":2381131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"買左張中古支那地圖，究竟係真定假","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:29:37.000Z","uid":200036,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c04d403b70298dad704659079ea3665ca09367","tid":2381131,"uid":200036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"日本bid 返黎嘅，幾舊水唔係咩值錢野<br />\n但屋企人見到話肯定係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話咁多年點會咁新淨，肯定比蟲蛀到渣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都啱但係睇墨水，紙質唔似現代野，而且有少少霉積<br />\n搞到我都半信半疑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDUysf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDUysf9.png&h=c8775dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Jon420.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Jon420.png&h=8b08c6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJon43c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJon43c.png&h=4cdb516b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcQE7gK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcQE7gK.png&h=81b71488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打們有無咩hints 張野係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗諗下上面仲寫住滿洲國，昭和11年又真係好難係真野<br />\n但係又唔係咩首版馬騮郵票咁張野仿黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申唔放純好奇，唔好留言話放左佢可以買首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611c63b74d0e171ca52bc13735b2c19fd3486810","tid":2381131,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"業餘考古師"},{"pid":"9c3b54505f18dfcc5bcdf90879cade9d5262224b","tid":2381131,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"新支那現勢圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746ac2